window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A world engulfed in flames. A future forged in blood. A chance to start over.</p> <p>Gabriel and the Reclaimers fight tooth and nail for humanity's survival. If only things were as simple as holding off a vast PAC army.</p> <p>The Winds of Destruction are blowing.</p> <p>Deadman's schemes blaze a path out of the shadows. Arcanists join the battle.</p> <p>Good thing Gabriel has begun mastering his powers. Too bad Command—in its infinite wisdom—chained the 42nd Company to an anomaly hunting unit.</p> <p>Outnumbered, outgunned, and outclassed, humanity's future is decided in fires of war…</p>"; 
